<h3 class='text-dark justify-content-center'> How to Calculate Interest </h3>
</div>
<div class= 'mb-3'><strong>Interest</strong> is the extra payment for saving or borrowing money. This is usually set by the lenders or commercial banks.</div>
<div class="container-fluid">
 <div class="row ml-0 mr-0">
