<br>
<strong>Principal (P)</strong> means amount of money saved or borrowed.
<br>
<strong>Rate (R) </strong> means the annual rate of the interest given as percentage.
<br>
<strong>Time (T)</strong> means the time (measure in year) for which the money is saved or borrowed.
<br>
