  <h3 class='text-dark justify-content-center'> Commodity Discounts </h3>
</div>
<p>
A <strong>discount</strong> is the money taken off the price of an item or commodity to encourage the buyer(s).
</p>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
